  <brief_title>Ph II Early BC Pre-Surgical Biologic Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A PreSurgical Study to Evaluate Molecular Alterations That Occur in Human Breast Cancer Tissue and Normal Skin After Short Term Exposure to ZD1839 (IRESSA) and to Correlate These Alterations With Pharmacokinetic Parameters.</official_title>
